<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #667eea;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #5568d3;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: white;
      border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .details {
      background: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .details dl {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .details dt {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .details dd {
      margin: 5px 0 10px 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>üéâ Your Backup is Ready!</h1>
    <p>Migration <%= @migration.token %></p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>Great news! Your account backup is now ready for download.</p>

    <div class="details">
      <dl>
        <dt>DID:</dt>
        <dd><code><%= @migration.did %></code></dd>

        <dt>Old Handle:</dt>
        <dd>@<%= @migration.old_handle %></dd>

        <dt>New Handle:</dt>
        <dd>@<%= @migration.new_handle %></dd>

        <% if @backup_size %>
        <dt>Backup Size:</dt>
        <dd><%= number_to_human_size(@backup_size) %></dd>
        <% end %>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @download_url %>" class="button">
        ‚¨áÔ∏è Download Your Backup
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">‚è∞ Important: 24-Hour Availability</h3>
      <p>This backup will be available for <strong>24 hours</strong> and will automatically be deleted after:</p>
      <p><strong><%= @expires_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %l:%M %p %Z') if @expires_at %></strong></p>
      <p>We recommend downloading it now for safekeeping.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">üì¶ What's in your backup?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Repository:</strong> All your posts, likes, follows, and profile data</li>
        <li><strong>Blobs:</strong> All images, videos, and media attachments</li>
        <li><strong>Metadata:</strong> Migration information and timestamps</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>What's Next?</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Download your backup</strong> (recommended for safekeeping)</li>
      <li>Your migration will <strong>continue automatically</strong> in the background</li>
      <li>Track progress at: <a href="<%= migration_url(@migration, token: @migration.token, host: ENV.fetch('DOMAIN', 'localhost:3001')) %>">Migration Status Page</a></li>
      <li>You'll be notified when ready for final activation</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Migration Token: <code><%= @migration.token %></code></p>
      <p>Eurosky Migration Service</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
